# School Portal Upgrade 5

This is **School Portal Upgrade 5**, a Node.js + Express + SQLite project with the following modules:

- Authentication (login, forgot/reset password)
- Admin (user management, CSV import, notifications)
- Teacher (results + attendance)
- Student (dashboard + report card + PIN-based results)
- Parent (view student results/attendance)
- Employment portal (jobs + applications)
- Attendance tracking
- Blog + Library (educational PDFs/apps)
- Notifications via Email (SMTP) / SMS (Twilio) â€” fallback to console logs
- Responsive design with hamburger menus

## ðŸš€ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/school-portal-upgrade-5.git
cd school-portal-upgrade-5
```

### 2. Install Dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Configure Environment
Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and update with your values:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

Set database, SMTP, Twilio, etc.

### 4. Seed Database
```bash
node seed.js
```

This ensures an **admin account** is created from `.env`.

### 5. Run Server
```bash
npm start
```

Then open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)

